              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900 group-hover:text-purple-600 transition-colors">Fiscalité Vente</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">Tout savoir sur la fiscalité et l'optimisation de votre vente</p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
                </svg>
                <span>32 pages • Format PDF</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-purple-600 font-semibold group-hover:gap-4 transition-all">
                <span>Télécharger gratuitement</span>
                <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
          </a>

          <!-- Guide 5 : Préparer -->
          <a href="/guides/preparer-maison" class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden border-2 border-orange-500/10 hover:border-orange-500/30">
            <div class="p-8">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500 to-orange-700 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
